{
  "id": "6983197aed38d151c1605dcc",
  "title": "ヤバい人達を見つけ出すX(Twitter)検索単語",
  "created": 1770199422,
  "updated": 1772971363,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6983197aed38d151c1605dcc",
      "text": "ヤバい人達を見つけ出すX(Twitter)検索単語",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199422,
      "updated": 1770289454
    },
    {
      "id": "698319810000000000ea6d59",
      "text": "ブロックし続けると無限に居ることを実感する[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199426,
      "updated": 1770199698
    },
    {
      "id": "698addc40000000000489e8b",
      "text": "\tキリがないかと思ったけど、全部ブロックできた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770708421,
      "updated": 1770708527
    },
    {
      "id": "698ade1c0000000000489e8c",
      "text": " \t全員ブロックし尽くすと「」の検索結果はありませんと出てくる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770708509,
      "updated": 1770708509
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfab40000000000c86ccb",
      "text": " 合計1000人くらい居るほか、毎日新しい人が登場する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770781365,
      "updated": 1770781411
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfae30000000000c86ccc",
      "text": "  新規アカウントというよりは、引っかかるフレーズを使っていなくて漏れていた人と思われる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770781411,
      "updated": 1770781421
    },
    {
      "id": "698ad1de0000000000489e89",
      "text": "単語を収集すると共通点を見いだせるかもしれない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770705375,
      "updated": 1770705385
    },
    {
      "id": "69831a5d0000000000ea6d65",
      "text": "Chrome拡張かなんかで自動的にやりたいな[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770199646,
      "updated": 1770796170
    },
    {
      "id": "698c62ba000000000009fc8c",
      "text": "\t昔 red block というものがあったらしい[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770807995,
      "updated": 1770808007
    },
    {
      "id": "698c62db000000000009fc8e",
      "text": "\t\t特定のアカウントをフォローしている人をまとめてブロックしたりできたとか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770808027,
      "updated": 1770808047
    },
    {
      "id": "698c34780000000000779a19",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796152,
      "updated": 1770796152
    },
    {
      "id": "69831b200000000000ea6d6a",
      "text": "病的",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199841,
      "updated": 1770199845
    },
    {
      "id": "698319820000000000ea6d5a",
      "text": " % 集団ストーカー",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199426,
      "updated": 1770780427
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf70f0000000000c86cb0",
      "text": "  [集団ストーカー]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780431,
      "updated": 1770780432
    },
    {
      "id": "6983ea9f0000000000672c53",
      "text": " % 電磁波攻撃",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770252960,
      "updated": 1770780428
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7120000000000c86cb1",
      "text": "  [電磁波攻撃]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780434,
      "updated": 1770780435
    },
    {
      "id": "6983198a0000000000ea6d5c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199435,
      "updated": 1770211173
    },
    {
      "id": "69831b440000000000ea6d70",
      "text": "敵対的",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199876,
      "updated": 1770199889
    },
    {
      "id": "698ab06c0000000000489e63",
      "text": " [フェミニズム]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770696813,
      "updated": 1770780438
    },
    {
      "id": "698ab02c0000000000489e56",
      "text": "  % フェミ -フェミニ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770781003,
      "updated": 1770781003
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf71d0000000000c86cb2",
      "text": "  \tフェミニズムの話とフェミニストの話を除外して[ツイフェミ]（[フェミ]）を罵る投稿だけを抽出する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770781004,
      "updated": 1770781030
    },
    {
      "id": "698ab02c0000000000489e57",
      "text": "  % アンフェ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770696749,
      "updated": 1770696818
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7210000000000c86cb3",
      "text": "   [アンチフェミニスト]の略",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780449,
      "updated": 1770781050
    },
    {
      "id": "69831b320000000000ea6d6e",
      "text": "  \t「[フェミニスト]」は学術的な意味合いも持つが、[アンフェ]は変な人しか見つからない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199858,
      "updated": 1770781058
    },
    {
      "id": "6983eaac0000000000672c54",
      "text": "  % チン騎士",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770252973,
      "updated": 1770696818
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7290000000000c86cb4",
      "text": "  [チン騎士]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780457,
      "updated": 1770780458
    },
    {
      "id": "69831b320000000000ea6d6f",
      "text": " 政治",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199858,
      "updated": 1771084863
    },
    {
      "id": "698ab07d0000000000489e64",
      "text": " \t% パヨク",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770696830,
      "updated": 1770696837
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7330000000000c86cb5",
      "text": "  \t[パヨク]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780466,
      "updated": 1770780468
    },
    {
      "id": "698ab0850000000000489e65",
      "text": " \t% ネトウヨ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770696838,
      "updated": 1770696841
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7370000000000c86cb6",
      "text": " \t\t[ネトウヨ]は概ね[罵倒語]だが、たまに真面目な議論方面で出てくることもある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780470,
      "updated": 1770781086
    },
    {
      "id": "698abec50000000000489e7a",
      "text": " \t% 反日",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770700486,
      "updated": 1770700794
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf73a0000000000c86cb7",
      "text": "  \t[反日]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780474,
      "updated": 1770780475
    },
    {
      "id": "698abffa0000000000489e85",
      "text": " \t\t[政治家]の[公式アカウント]がたまに巻き込まれる（それはそれで[品がない]政治家だ）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770700794,
      "updated": 1770781126
    },
    {
      "id": "698acb7b0000000000489e86",
      "text": " \t% 売国",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770703740,
      "updated": 1770703744
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7420000000000c86cb8",
      "text": "  \t[売国]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780482,
      "updated": 1770780482
    },
    {
      "id": "69909c4500000000003470a6",
      "text": "  % \"不正選挙\"",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771084870,
      "updated": 1771084870
    },
    {
      "id": "69909c4500000000003470a7",
      "text": "   [不正選挙]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771084870,
      "updated": 1771084870
    },
    {
      "id": "69909c4500000000003470a8",
      "text": "  \tダブルクオーテーションで囲むことで1つのフレーズとして扱う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771084870,
      "updated": 1771084870
    },
    {
      "id": "69909c4500000000003470a9",
      "text": "  % 出ていけ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771084870,
      "updated": 1771084870
    },
    {
      "id": "69909c4500000000003470aa",
      "text": "  \t明確な排外的主張",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771084870,
      "updated": 1771084870
    },
    {
      "id": "69909c4500000000003470ab",
      "text": "  \t独特な用語ではないにも関わらず、かなりのヒット率を",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771084870,
      "updated": 1771084870
    },
    {
      "id": "69909c4500000000003470ac",
      "text": "  % 日本から出ていけ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771084870,
      "updated": 1771084870
    },
    {
      "id": "69909c4500000000003470ad",
      "text": "  \t明確な排外的主張",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771084870,
      "updated": 1771084870
    },
    {
      "id": "69909c4500000000003470ae",
      "text": "  \tヒット率が上がる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771084870,
      "updated": 1771084870
    },
    {
      "id": "69909c4500000000003470af",
      "text": "  \tテンプレみたいにこの言葉を吐き捨てる人が多い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771084870,
      "updated": 1771084870
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3361000000000011ee2f",
      "text": " \t% 表現の自由戦士",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772958561,
      "updated": 1772971363
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad3375000000000011ee30",
      "text": " \t\t[表現の自由]に関連して、一部の面々を揶揄する表現",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1772958582,
      "updated": 1772958628
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad33a7000000000011ee32",
      "text": " \t\t主に[表現の自由]のことしか考えない面々を指して揶揄しているような印象",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1772958632,
      "updated": 1772958660
    },
    {
      "id": "698abec70000000000489e7d",
      "text": " その他",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770700488,
      "updated": 1771084870
    },
    {
      "id": "698ab0c30000000000489e77",
      "text": "  % 反ワク",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770696900,
      "updated": 1770696910
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7450000000000c86cb9",
      "text": "   [反ワク]:  [反ワクチン]派の略であり蔑称",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780485,
      "updated": 1770781150
    },
    {
      "id": "698abf370000000000489e83",
      "text": "  % オールドメディア",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770700600,
      "updated": 1770700600
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7490000000000c86cba",
      "text": "   [オールドメディア]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780489,
      "updated": 1770780489
    },
    {
      "id": "698ad1d30000000000489e87",
      "text": "  % マスゴミ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770705364,
      "updated": 1770705364
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf74d0000000000c86cbb",
      "text": "   [マスゴミ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780492,
      "updated": 1770780493
    },
    {
      "id": "698ad1d40000000000489e88",
      "text": "  % 拡散希望 被害",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770705364,
      "updated": 1771084868
    },
    {
      "id": "698abf370000000000489e84",
      "text": "   [拡散希望] [被害]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770700600,
      "updated": 1771083503
    },
    {
      "id": "698ab0c20000000000489e75",
      "text": "  　[声がでかい]個人がいっぱい出てくる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770696899,
      "updated": 1770696899
    },
    {
      "id": "698ab0c20000000000489e76",
      "text": "  　（全てとまでは言わないが）偏った情報で真偽不明な上、[共感ビジネス]に近しいものが多いので関わらないのがよさげ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770696899,
      "updated": 1770696899
    },
    {
      "id": "698ab0b40000000000489e67",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770696885,
      "updated": 1770696885
    },
    {
      "id": "69831b5e0000000000ea6d71",
      "text": "貧困ビジネス系",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199902,
      "updated": 1770200005
    },
    {
      "id": "6983198f0000000000ea6d5e",
      "text": " % 個人融資 即金",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199439,
      "updated": 1770253040
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7640000000000c86cbe",
      "text": "  [個人融資] [即金]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780516,
      "updated": 1770780519
    },
    {
      "id": "698319a80000000000ea6d5f",
      "text": " \t[闇バイト]？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199464,
      "updated": 1770199927
    },
    {
      "id": "698319ae0000000000ea6d60",
      "text": "  [貧困ビジネス]？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199471,
      "updated": 1770199927
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfa0a0000000000c86cc6",
      "text": " % 即金",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770781194,
      "updated": 1770781196
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfa0f0000000000c86cc7",
      "text": "  [即金]単体でも精度良く見つかる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770781198,
      "updated": 1770781208
    },
    {
      "id": "6983eafe0000000000672c55",
      "text": " $ 即日",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770253054,
      "updated": 1770781194
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7780000000000c86cbf",
      "text": "  [即日]:  即金と一緒で貧困釣り",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780535,
      "updated": 1770781171
    },
    {
      "id": "6983eb270000000000672c57",
      "text": " \t即日〇〇したと呟いているだけの一般人が巻き込まれる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770253096,
      "updated": 1770253112
    },
    {
      "id": "698319ca0000000000ea6d62",
      "text": " % チャトレ メルレ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199499,
      "updated": 1770253037
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf77f0000000000c86cc0",
      "text": "  [チャトレ] [メルレ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780542,
      "updated": 1770780547
    },
    {
      "id": "698319e60000000000ea6d63",
      "text": " \t[チャットレディ]、[メールレディ]の略",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199526,
      "updated": 1770780556
    },
    {
      "id": "698319f10000000000ea6d64",
      "text": " \t金欠なのか無限に湧いている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199538,
      "updated": 1770199927
    },
    {
      "id": "698319860000000000ea6d5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199430,
      "updated": 1770199430
    },
    {
      "id": "6983ea9b0000000000672c52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770252956,
      "updated": 1770252956
    },
    {
      "id": "69835e320000000000a3aed9",
      "text": "[詐欺]・[犯罪]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1770217009,
      "updated": 1770218887
    },
    {
      "id": "698364ea0000000000a3aeea",
      "text": " [*** 危]ないので見るだけにして関わらないこと",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1770218729,
      "updated": 1770807514
    },
    {
      "id": "698365970000000000a3aeed",
      "text": " こういう手口がある程度に留めておくのが良い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770218902,
      "updated": 1770708415
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfa4b0000000000c86cc8",
      "text": " 貧困ビジネスと詐欺・犯罪の区別は難しい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770781258,
      "updated": 1770781288
    },
    {
      "id": "69835e420000000000a3aedc",
      "text": "　% お金 余った フォロー",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770217025,
      "updated": 1770780752
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7a10000000000c86cc1",
      "text": " 　[お金が余った] [フォロー]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780576,
      "updated": 1770780603
    },
    {
      "id": "69835ecb0000000000a3aedf",
      "text": "　　「お金が余ったから」という口実で常識に疎い人を釣ろうとする系のツイートが見つかる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1770217163,
      "updated": 1770217253
    },
    {
      "id": "6983637f0000000000a3aee6",
      "text": "　　当然支払われない。",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1770218366,
      "updated": 1770219373
    },
    {
      "id": "6983676e00000000009745b7",
      "text": "　　相手からすると支払うメリットは一切ないが、犯罪に使える馬鹿が釣れるメリットはある",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1770219373,
      "updated": 1770219373
    },
    {
      "id": "69835f400000000000a3aee1",
      "text": "　　[闇バイト]の入り口になってしまうとかなんとか",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1770217279,
      "updated": 1770217309
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf7dc0000000000c86cc2",
      "text": "　　[前澤社長]が[お金配り]をしてしまったため[カモ釣り]法のヒントを与えてしまったように見える",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780636,
      "updated": 1770780721
    },
    {
      "id": "698c60f90000000000404e95",
      "text": "　　　（騙される側の常識の無さを踏まえても）お金配りでほんとに配られるという前例作ったのも良くなかったと思う[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1770807542,
      "updated": 1770807623
    },
    {
      "id": "698c630a000000000009fc8f",
      "text": " 　　　+1[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770808074,
      "updated": 1770808084
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf83b0000000000c86cc3",
      "text": "　% 高収入 簡単 副業 在宅",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780730,
      "updated": 1770780758
    },
    {
      "id": "698bf83b0000000000c86cc4",
      "text": " 　[高収入] [簡単] [副業] [在宅]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770780730,
      "updated": 1770780743
    },
    {
      "id": "698364cf0000000000a3aee7",
      "text": "　　誰でも高収入の謳い文句でLINEや外部サイト等に誘導するアカウントが多数出てくる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770218704,
      "updated": 1770780730
    },
    {
      "id": "698365810000000000a3aeec",
      "text": "　　[クローズド]（閉鎖的）な場所に誘い込まれる為、そのまま[詐欺]に遭う可能性が高い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770218880,
      "updated": 1770780875
    },
    {
      "id": "698365da0000000000a3aeee",
      "text": "　　「誰にも相談させない」は[特殊詐欺]の基本である",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1770218969,
      "updated": 1770219065
    },
    {
      "id": "698ae9ab000000000077c6f0",
      "text": "　% いいね&フォロー&\"した人にだけ\"",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770711468,
      "updated": 1770711475
    },
    {
      "id": "698ae9bc000000000077c6f1",
      "text": "　\t[囲い込み]、[個別誘導]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770711485,
      "updated": 1770780901
    },
    {
      "id": "69835e320000000000a3aeda",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1770217009,
      "updated": 1770217009
    },
    {
      "id": "6983ea8f0000000000672c51",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770252944,
      "updated": 1770252944
    },
    {
      "id": "69831c050000000000ea6d73",
      "text": "[株価操縦]（[仕手]）系",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770200070,
      "updated": 1770780919
    },
    {
      "id": "6983ea480000000000672c4f",
      "text": " % \"スーパーインサイダー\"",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770252873,
      "updated": 1770253005
    },
    {
      "id": "6983ea550000000000672c50",
      "text": "  [インサイダー情報]がホイホイ漏れるわけがない上に、修飾語としてスーパーをつけている面白フレーズ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770252886,
      "updated": 1770780924
    },
    {
      "id": "69831bfe0000000000ea6d72",
      "text": " % \"で必ず買い\"",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770200063,
      "updated": 1770696945
    },
    {
      "id": "698c633d000000000009fc90",
      "text": " \t株を〇〇円でで必ず買うわけが無いのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770808126,
      "updated": 1770808203
    },
    {
      "id": "698c6354000000000009fc91",
      "text": " \tあるいは、いくらでで必ず買えという意味なら余計に悪い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770808148,
      "updated": 1770808189
    },
    {
      "id": "69831f730000000000ea6d75",
      "text": " \tテンプレ文コピペみたいになっているので乗っ取りスパムか、謎の業者がやっているのかもしれない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770200947,
      "updated": 1770201019
    },
    {
      "id": "69833de50000000000ea6d76",
      "text": " \tリプ欄にインプレゾンビが大量に湧いていることからも謎の業者が絡んでいる感じがする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770208742,
      "updated": 1770208779
    },
    {
      "id": "6983ea2e0000000000672c4e",
      "text": " \tグッズとかを必ず買う宣言している一般人が巻き込まれる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770252847,
      "updated": 1770252865
    },
    {
      "id": "698ab0f80000000000489e79",
      "text": " \t先頭に「で」をつけると「きゃーこのグッズ素敵！必ず買います！」みたいな投稿を弾ける",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770696953,
      "updated": 1770696980
    },
    {
      "id": "6983e9ec0000000000672c4b",
      "text": " % \"一度だけ言う\"",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770252780,
      "updated": 1770253010
    },
    {
      "id": "6983e9f20000000000672c4c",
      "text": "  「必ず買い」テンプレの中に入っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770252787,
      "updated": 1770252817
    },
    {
      "id": "6983ea1b0000000000672c4d",
      "text": "  テンション高くなってしまった一般人が巻き込まれる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770252828,
      "updated": 1770252840
    },
    {
      "id": "69831aaa0000000000ea6d66",
      "text": " % 銘柄コード",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770199723,
      "updated": 1770711523
    },
    {
      "id": "698aebbf000000000077c6f2",
      "text": " % 来るよ。大急騰...",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770712000,
      "updated": 1770712004
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfd070000000000c86ccd",
      "text": " % 誰でも簡単に利益",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770781960,
      "updated": 1770781964
    },
    {
      "id": "698423b70000000000672c58",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770267576,
      "updated": 1770267576
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfecb0000000000c86cd1",
      "text": "インプレゾンビ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770782412,
      "updated": 1770782414
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfedf0000000000c86cd5",
      "text": "\t上手くいくかは未検証",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770782431,
      "updated": 1770782431
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfece0000000000c86cd2",
      "text": "  % \"888\" filter:replies",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770782414,
      "updated": 1770782663
    },
    {
      "id": "698bffca0000000000c86cd6",
      "text": "  \t一言だけリプライしている物を探す。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770782666,
      "updated": 1770782709
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfff40000000000c86cd7",
      "text": "  \tリプライ元もおかしいのでまとめて処理できる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770782709,
      "updated": 1770782730
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfedb0000000000c86cd4",
      "text": "  % 👍️ \"888\" filter:replies",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770782428,
      "updated": 1770782697
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfaa00000000000c86cca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770781345,
      "updated": 1770781345
    },
    {
      "id": "698c942e0000000000297c77",
      "text": "出会系・アダルト",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770820654,
      "updated": 1770820664
    },
    {
      "id": "698c94370000000000297c7a",
      "text": "\t% #いいねでDM",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770820664,
      "updated": 1770820675
    },
    {
      "id": "698c94440000000000297c7b",
      "text": " \t尋常ではない流速にビビる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770820677,
      "updated": 1770820711
    },
    {
      "id": "698c94670000000000297c7d",
      "text": " \t人口が多すぎる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770820711,
      "updated": 1770820725
    },
    {
      "id": "698c94330000000000297c79",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770820660,
      "updated": 1770820660
    },
    {
      "id": "698c942e0000000000297c78",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770820654,
      "updated": 1770820654
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfa9d0000000000c86cc9",
      "text": "その他",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770781342,
      "updated": 1770781344
    },
    {
      "id": "69840f5800000000006f13ab",
      "text": " % 何度でも言う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770262361,
      "updated": 1770781348
    },
    {
      "id": "69840f8e00000000006f13ad",
      "text": " % 実は",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770262414,
      "updated": 1770781348
    },
    {
      "id": "698423bf0000000000672c59",
      "text": " \t一般人も言ってる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770267584,
      "updated": 1770781348
    },
    {
      "id": "69840f9100000000006f13ae",
      "text": " % 炎上覚悟だけど",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770262417,
      "updated": 1770781348
    },
    {
      "id": "698c61c10000000000404e97",
      "text": " 　言うほど注目されてない人（誰コイツ）も言ってるのもポイント[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1770807743,
      "updated": 1770807770
    },
    {
      "id": "69840f9500000000006f13af",
      "text": " % プロフ見て",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770262422,
      "updated": 1770781348
    },
    {
      "id": "69840f9800000000006f13b0",
      "text": " % 固定ポスト見て",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770262424,
      "updated": 1770781348
    },
    {
      "id": "69840f6400000000006f13ac",
      "text": " \t見たら謎が解けるよ！とか書いてたりする[who.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770262373,
      "updated": 1770781348
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfec60000000000c86cd0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770782406,
      "updated": 1770782406
    },
    {
      "id": "698bfec40000000000c86ccf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1770782404,
      "updated": 1770782404
    }
  ]
}